comments: Chriss (GSW) moves alongside of Lowry (TOR)  defending his drive and maintains legal position contesting his driving shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) is already in Paschall's (GSW) path and makes marginal contact during the pick as they disengage.
Curry (GSW) makes marginal contact with Siakam's (TOR) arm that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Siakam (TOR) jumps from A to B into the body of Curry (GSW) and affects his driving shot attempt.
Powell (TOR) establishes legal position in Paschall's (GSW) path during the pick and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Lee (GSW) is not in a legal guarding position and he turns his body into Siakam (TOR) and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Chriss (GSW) establishes legal position in Powell's (TOR) path during the pick and absorbs the contact.
The Raptors are awarded a timeout prior to any possible foul is committed.
Ibaka (TOR) establishes legal position in Lee's (GSW) path and makes slight contact as they disengage.
Siakam (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Lee's (GSW) path and absorbs the contact.
Lee (GSW) cleanly dislodges the ball from Powell (TOR) during his drive.
Powell (TOR) moves into Lee (GSW) after he secures the ball and the contact affects his SQBR.
Siakam (TOR) makes marginal contact with Chriss (GSW) that does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it is determined that the foul on Lee (GSW) is a clear path foul.
Lee (GSW) commits a take foul on Powell (TOR).
Siakam (TOR) briefly engages and separates with Bender (GSW).
